 data-type if it can be cast safely, otherwise raise an error.
 The requirements, if given, are a sequence containing the requested combination
 of the flags 'C_CONTIGUOUS' ('C'), 'F_CONTIGUOUS' ('F'), 'ALIGNED' ('A'),
