\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{A}=\mathbf{U\boldsymbol{\Sigma}}\mathbf{V}^{H}$
\end_inset

.
 The only non-zero portion of 
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{\Sigma}$
\end_inset

