 Because it is so widely used, the full pdf with the location 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(\mu\right)$
\end_inset

 and scale 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(\sigma\right)$
\end_inset

 parameters is provided:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
